Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.62,0:01:47.60,Title,,0,0,250,,{\fad(200,200)}Carta de Triunfo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.59,0:01:53.49,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,Princesa Mansherry, espero que você esteja segura.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.63,0:01:55.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Incrível!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.80,0:01:58.27,Main,,0,0,0,,Você consegue ver o interior do \Npalácio daqui?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.27,0:02:00.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Sim, com minha clarividência.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.25,0:02:01.97,Main,,0,0,0,,Posso projetar minha visão para qualquer lugar.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.97,0:02:04.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Sanji morreria para ter sua habilidade.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.80,0:02:08.44,Main,,0,0,0,,Como será a Princesa Mansherry?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.44,0:02:14.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Se não me engano, Leo disse que ela é \Ncaprichosa, egoísta e mesquinha.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.25,0:02:16.77,Main,,0,0,0,,Quem diabos é você?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.77,0:02:18.42,Main,,0,0,0,,Pare, por favor!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.16,0:02:21.55,Main,,0,0,0,,K-Kin'emon!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.55,0:02:23.57,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, Usopp-dono!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.57,0:02:24.46,Main,,0,0,0,,Você o conhece?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.46,0:02:26.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Sim, deixe-o passar...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.73,0:02:29.55,Main,,0,0,0,,Tem um cara estranho!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.55,0:02:34.13,Main,,0,0,0,,É Kanjuro, a pessoa que\N eu estava procurando.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.13,0:02:37.86,Main,,0,0,0,,O que é essa criatura tão patética?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.38,0:02:45.88,Main,,0,0,0,,Bem, acabamos de emergir\N e fomos surpreendidos...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.88,0:02:48.15,Main,,0,0,0,,...pela multidão que se aproximava...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.15,0:02:50.78,Main,,0,0,0,,...desse platô, então estávamos\N nos perguntando o que estava acontecendo.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.78,0:02:52.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Ah, certo!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.76,0:02:55.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Acho que eles não podem subir até aqui, mas...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.76,0:02:58.96,Main,,0,0,0,,Não se desespere, diabinho de nariz comprido!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.96,0:03:00.96,Main,,0,0,0,,Eles estavam com problemas, então...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.96,0:03:03.36,Main,,0,0,0,,...eu fiz uma rede para eles!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.36,0:03:04.35,Main,,0,0,0,,O quê?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.76,0:03:08.41,Main,,0,0,0,,Eles chegarão a qualquer momento.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.41,0:03:11.96,Main,,0,0,0,,Por que você fez isso, idiota?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.96,0:03:13.98,Main,,0,0,0,,Vamos capturar o Deus Usopp!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.77,0:03:16.47,Main,,0,0,0,,Essa corda é horrível!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.47,0:03:19.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Esses caras vêm atrás da minha cabeça!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.25,0:03:21.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Minha ajuda foi desnecessária?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.25,0:03:23.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Que idiota eu fui...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.89,0:03:25.40,Main,,0,0,0,,Que bagunça!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.40,0:03:27.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Falhei com meu salvador!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.31,0:03:30.29,Main,,0,0,0,,Vou fazer harakiri para mostrar meu arrependimento!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.29,0:03:31.93,Main,,0,0,0,,Não faça isso, Kanjuro!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.93,0:03:33.13,Main,,0,0,0,,Tudo bem, então não farei.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.13,0:03:34.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Cala a boca! Faça!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.33,0:03:36.31,Main,,0,0,0,,O que vamos fazer com esses escaladores?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.30,0:03:38.84,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,Talvez...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.60,0:03:43.31,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,Eu não olhei naquele quarto!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.67,0:03:53.66,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170\pos(1010,169)}ASCENDENDO ACIMA\N DO NÍVEL 2
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.67,0:03:53.66,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170\pos(190,95)}EQUIPE DE\N REBECCA E ROBIN
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.22,0:03:59.01,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Leo, você me escuta?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.01,0:04:00.19,Main,,0,0,0,,Sim, Viola-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.19,0:04:02.42,Main,,0,0,0,,Eu encontrei a Princesa Mansherry!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.42,0:04:03.81,Main,,0,0,0,,No palácio!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.81,0:04:06.39,Main,,0,0,0,,A Princesa Mansherry \Nestá no palácio!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.39,0:04:07.53,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Que alívio!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.53,0:04:09.13,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Em que parte do palácio?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.13,0:04:12.70,Main,,0,0,0,,No quartinho atrás da capela.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.70,0:04:14.07,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Você se lembra?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.61,0:04:15.61,Main,,0,0,0,,Um quarto...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.37,0:04:17.59,Main,,0,0,0,,...pequeno?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.59,0:04:19.30,Main,,0,0,0,,A sala das travessuras!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.30,0:04:21.15,Main,,0,0,0,,Sim, lá!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.93,0:04:24.08,Main,,0,0,0,,Acabei de me lembrar de Scarlett-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.08,0:04:25.51,Main,,0,0,0,,Minha mãe?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.51,0:04:26.65,Main,,0,0,0,,Sim...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.37,0:04:30.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Quando íamos ao palácio,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.76,0:04:33.86,Main,,0,0,0,,fazíamos travessuras com Viola-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.86,0:04:36.38,Main,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,1038)}...e o Rei Riku nos repreendia!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.19,0:04:39.81,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Irmã!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.81,0:04:41.40,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Scarlett-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.81,0:04:41.40,Secondary,,0,0,0,,Scarlett-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.45,0:04:45.25,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Você foi repreendida de novo?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.25,0:04:46.26,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Você nunca aprende.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.26,0:04:47.59,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Não é isso!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.59,0:04:50.31,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Leo e os outros dois quebraram um prato!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.31,0:04:52.97,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Você disse que podíamos quebrá-lo!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.97,0:04:56.48,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Não, eu disse que podiam tocá-lo!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.48,0:04:57.84,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,O quê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.48,0:04:57.84,Secondary,,0,0,0,,O quê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.42,0:05:04.85,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Vou pedir desculpas com você mais tarde.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.85,0:05:06.44,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Sério?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.44,0:05:07.29,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Sim.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.29,0:05:09.80,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Bem, vocês estão com fome?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.80,0:05:11.83,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Sim!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.80,0:05:11.83,Secondary,,0,0,0,,Sim!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.96,0:05:19.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Nós todos amávamos muito a Scarlett-sama...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.10,0:05:20.28,Main,,0,0,0,,Sim!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.28,0:05:23.56,Main,,0,0,0,,Ela sempre foi tão gentil \Ne doce conosco...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.28,0:05:36.04,Main,,0,0,0,,Ainda me lembro bem da sala das travessuras!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.04,0:05:37.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Obrigado pela informação!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.72,0:05:40.67,Main,,0,0,0,,Agora o palácio é o bastião do inimigo.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.67,0:05:42.45,Main,,0,0,0,,Tenha cuidado, Leo!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.45,0:05:43.73,Main,,0,0,0,,Entendido!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.73,0:05:45.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Vamos salvar nossa\N princesa, custe o que custar!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.05,0:05:55.70,Main,,0,0,0,,Esses caras...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.07,0:06:06.36,Main,,0,0,0,,Estamos sobrevoando o terceiro nível, Rebecca!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.36,0:06:07.97,Main,,0,0,0,,Sim, Robin-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.97,0:06:09.55,Main,,0,0,0,,O campo de flores está no próximo!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.74,0:06:13.94,Main,,0,0,0,,Algo está vindo voando de baixo!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.94,0:06:20.56,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,Os verdadeiros Chapéus de Palha são muito mais incríveis do que eu imaginava...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.66,0:06:27.43,Main,,0,0,0,,Gallo-kun, cuidado!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.70,0:06:31.07,Main,,0,0,0,,Punk Bala!{balas explosivas}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.01,0:06:38.21,Main,,0,0,0,,Gallo-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.35,0:06:44.24,Main,,0,0,0,,Essa é a habilidade da Pamu Pamu no Mi!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.78,0:06:47.68,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, não!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.68,0:06:50.23,Main,,0,0,0,,Meus besouros amarelos...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.93,0:06:54.93,Main,,0,0,0,,Robin-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.93,0:06:59.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Não acredito que há um grupo\N tentando chegar ao palácio assim!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.80,0:07:00.94,Main,,0,0,0,,É Gladius!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.94,0:07:02.27,Main,,0,0,0,,Punk...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.27,0:07:04.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Dez Fleur!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.71,0:07:12.39,Main,,0,0,0,,Rebecca, leve a chave\N para o campo de flores!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.39,0:07:14.21,Main,,0,0,0,,Eu vou ficar bem!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.21,0:07:15.28,Main,,0,0,0,,Robin-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.22,0:07:23.05,Main,,0,0,0,,Esses brinquedos...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.05,0:07:24.23,Main,,0,0,0,,Não me diga que...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.34,0:07:30.53,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170\pos(640,365)\fad(200,200)}ANTIGO PLANALTO\N DO PALÁCIO REAL
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.00,0:07:30.53,Main,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ambos são responsáveis.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.53,0:07:32.04,Main,,0,0,0,,Isso é...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.79,0:07:33.99,Main,,0,0,0,,O que está acontecendo?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.99,0:07:36.62,Main,,0,0,0,,Ainda está procurando algo, Viola?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.62,0:07:38.24,Main,,0,0,0,,Sugar acordou!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.24,0:07:39.81,Main,,0,0,0,,O quê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.81,0:07:40.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Ei!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.91,0:07:42.13,Main,,0,0,0,,O que você está dizendo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.13,0:07:42.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Sugar...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.21,0:07:47.81,Main,,0,0,0,,...tinha ficado completamente nocauteada\N depois do meu Hissatsu Ganmen Bikkuri Bako,{caixa surpresa com cara letal ou algo assim}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.81,0:07:51.02,Main,,0,0,0,,e parecia que não acordaria por vários dias...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.88,0:07:55.62,Main,,0,0,0,,Chapéu de Palha e companhia não\N sabem sobre sua existência, certo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.32,0:07:57.83,Main,,0,0,0,,Nem sobre sua habilidade.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.83,0:07:59.81,Main,,0,0,0,,Sugar se recuperou completamente!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.81,0:08:01.40,Main,,0,0,0,,Chapéu de Palha e companhia estão em perigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.70,0:08:07.65,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170\pos(700,365)\fad(200,200)}PALÁCIO REAL
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.10,0:08:18.01,Main,,0,0,0,,Q-Que todos que têm\N o nariz comprido se afastem!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.01,0:08:20.32,Main,,0,0,0,,Que todos morram!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.47,0:08:23.75,Main,,0,0,0,,Pensei que você estivesse com fome, então trouxe...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.75,0:08:24.76,Main,,0,0,0,,...isso.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.68,0:08:29.19,Main,,0,0,0,,São apenas salsichas.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.19,0:08:31.65,Main,,0,0,0,,Não me tragam coisas com forma alongada!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.65,0:08:33.57,Main,,0,0,0,,Os aperitivos devem ser uvas!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.57,0:08:34.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Você é idiota?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.63,0:08:39.70,Main,,0,0,0,,Transforme-se em uma brinquedo como os outros e vá lutar!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.22,0:08:46.68,Main,,0,0,0,,Desculpe, jovem mestre...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.62,0:08:50.69,Main,,0,0,0,,Vou transformar todo o país...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.23,0:08:53.14,Main,,0,0,0,,...em brinquedos de novo!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.14,0:08:57.65,Main,,0,0,0,,E vou começar com aquele nariz\N comprido irritante e seus companheiros,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.65,0:08:59.67,Main,,0,0,0,,os Chapéus de Palha!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.67,0:09:06.00,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170\pos(640,545)\fad(486,245)}PLANALTO DO PALÁCIO REAL
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.67,0:09:06.00,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\pos(935,90)}{\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170\fad(200,200)}GRUPO DE LUFFY
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.29,0:09:09.56,Main,,0,0,0,,Esquive, Farul!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.58,0:09:12.60,Main,,0,0,0,,Cavalo!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.60,0:09:14.44,Main,,0,0,0,,Maldito!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.44,0:09:15.81,Main,,0,0,0,,Gomu Gomu no...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.81,0:09:17.15,Main,,0,0,0,,...Jet Pistol!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.15,0:09:18.08,Main,,0,0,0,,Farul!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.51,0:09:21.81,Main,,0,0,0,,Aguente!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.81,0:09:23.48,Main,,0,0,0,,Que mandíbula poderosa!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.48,0:09:25.41,Main,,0,0,0,,Esmagou a cabeça dele!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.41,0:09:26.51,Main,,0,0,0,,Não morra, Farul!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.79,0:09:35.64,Main,,0,0,0,,Esse cara...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.64,0:09:37.51,Main,,0,0,0,,Mas eu fiz um buraco na barriga dele!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.51,0:09:38.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Maldito seja!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.37,0:09:39.90,Main,,0,0,0,,Como você pôde fazer isso com o Farul?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.90,0:09:43.04,Main,,0,0,0,,Biken: Round Table!{espada da beleza: mesa redonda, revisar primeira parte}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.86,0:09:55.57,Main,,0,0,0,,O quê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.75,0:10:14.99,Main,,0,0,0,,Eles são invencíveis?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.53,0:10:17.24,Main,,0,0,0,,Gomu Gomu no...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.24,0:10:19.60,Main,,0,0,0,,...UFO!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.83,0:10:59.85,Main,,0,0,0,,Droga!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.85,0:11:01.84,Main,,0,0,0,,Se ao menos eu tivesse as\Nchaves dessas algemas,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.84,0:11:03.51,Main,,0,0,0,,eu poderia cuidar de todos!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.94,0:11:08.68,Main,,0,0,0,,Algo está caindo do céu!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.42,0:11:13.82,Main,,0,0,0,,Eu baixei a guarda...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.82,0:11:14.87,Main,,0,0,0,,Cresta!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.87,0:11:17.42,Main,,0,0,0,,Essa voz é do Luffy-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.42,0:11:18.41,Main,,0,0,0,,Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.97,0:11:21.61,Main,,0,0,0,,Luffy, Tral-kun! Vocês estavam aqui?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.61,0:11:24.12,Main,,0,0,0,,Nico-ya, onde está minha chave?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.12,0:11:25.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Me dê agora mesmo!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.28,0:11:27.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Ela escapou...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.10,0:11:31.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Bem, uma garotinha sozinha...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.91,0:11:36.16,Main,,0,0,0,,...não poderia fazer nada \Nmesmo que chegasse ao palácio.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.71,0:11:39.59,Main,,0,0,0,,Vou persegui-la e matá-la depois.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.59,0:11:41.44,Main,,0,0,0,,Meu nome é Gladius.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.56,0:11:44.84,Main,,0,0,0,,Primeiro vou cuidar de todos vocês.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.52,0:11:47.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Deixe-os conosco.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.80,0:11:49.12,Main,,0,0,0,,Sim!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.12,0:11:49.96,Main,,0,0,0,,Hein?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.77,0:11:52.69,Main,,0,0,0,,Luffy! Tral-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.69,0:11:53.78,Main,,0,0,0,,E também Soldado-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.78,0:11:54.93,Main,,0,0,0,,Avancem!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.93,0:11:57.13,Main,,0,0,0,,Vão para o campo de flores, no quarto nível!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.13,0:11:58.03,Main,,0,0,0,,Isso mesmo!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.03,0:11:58.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Robin?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.40,0:12:01.84,Main,,0,0,0,,Rebecca está esperando por vocês!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.84,0:12:02.56,Main,,0,0,0,,Depressa!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.64,0:12:07.55,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,330)}{\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170\fad(200,200)}CAMPO DE FLORES\NPLANALTO DO PALÁCIO REAL\NQUARTO NÍVEL
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.88,0:12:09.84,Main,,0,0,0,,Chegamos ao quarto nível!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.84,0:12:13.11,Main,,0,0,0,,Será que Robin-san e os outros estão bem?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.11,0:12:14.99,Main,,0,0,0,,Sei que estão!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.99,0:12:17.32,Main,,0,0,0,,Os companheiros de Usoland são fortes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.30,0:12:20.12,Main,,0,0,0,,Sim, você está certo!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.12,0:12:24.53,Main,,0,0,0,,Rebecca-sama, temos que ir\N salvar a Princesa Mansherry!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.53,0:12:25.54,Main,,0,0,0,,Sim!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.54,0:12:27.96,Main,,0,0,0,,Está tudo bem em deixar você aqui sozinha?{tratamento, revisa, ryu}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.96,0:12:29.17,Main,,0,0,0,,Não tem problema!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.17,0:12:31.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Lucy e os outros virão logo!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.37,0:12:32.54,Main,,0,0,0,,Vão salvá-la!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.54,0:12:35.41,Main,,0,0,0,,Entendo, Rebecca-sama, \Ncuide-se você também.{tratamento, revisa, ryu :D}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.41,0:12:36.97,Main,,0,0,0,,Sim!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.02,0:12:53.02,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,Meu pai também deve estar em algum\N lugar deste campo de batalha...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.27,0:13:11.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Alguém chegou, hein?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.20,0:13:18.06,Main,,0,0,0,,É você...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.80,0:13:23.72,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\pos(380,180)}{\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170\fs22}PLANALTO DO PALÁCIO REAL\NTERCEIRO NÍVEL\NPALÁCIO REAL {PACE ONLY}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.05,0:13:26.42,Main,,0,0,0,,Gomu Gomu no...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.42,0:13:28.97,Main,,0,0,0,,Luffy-senpai, deixe comigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.97,0:13:29.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Crista de galo!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.72,0:13:30.82,Main,,0,0,0,,Barreira!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.53,0:13:39.89,Main,,0,0,0,,São balas explosivas!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.89,0:13:42.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Elas vão explodir antes que\N você consiga rebatê-las!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.00,0:13:43.67,Main,,0,0,0,,Nossa, que legal!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.59,0:13:47.51,Main,,0,0,0,,Não, não!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.51,0:13:50.01,Main,,0,0,0,,Não mereço tantos elogios!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.62,0:13:51.88,Main,,0,0,0,,Bartolomeo...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.88,0:13:54.71,Main,,0,0,0,,Barrier-bility: Stairs!{Barrihabilidade/Barrerabilidade: Escadaria/Escadas}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.91,0:14:18.90,Main,,0,0,0,,Incrível, isso é muito útil!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.90,0:14:21.40,Main,,0,0,0,,Use-as, por favor, Luffy-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.40,0:14:23.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Para onde você está olhando?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.38,0:14:24.74,Main,,0,0,0,,Obrigado, crista de galo!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.31,0:14:34.05,Main,,0,0,0,,Não mereço!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.05,0:14:38.93,Main,,0,0,0,,Sou eu quem deve agradecer\N por você ter nascido!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.93,0:14:40.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Bem!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.20,0:14:42.56,Main,,0,0,0,,Podemos ir direto para o quarto nível por aqui!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.56,0:14:43.84,Main,,0,0,0,,Vamos, Tral!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.84,0:14:44.77,Main,,0,0,0,,Vamos!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.58,0:15:01.18,Main,,0,0,0,,Soldado!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.46,0:15:02.85,Main,,0,0,0,,Eu vou na frente!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.88,0:15:05.48,Main,,0,0,0,,Espere, Soldado!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.48,0:15:09.15,Main,,0,0,0,,Cabbage!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.15,0:15:11.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Eu vou segurá-los aqui!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.33,0:15:13.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Continue avançando, Chapéu de Palha!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.77,0:15:16.23,Main,,0,0,0,,Derrotaram meu querido \Ncavalo neste nível!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.56,0:15:22.70,Main,,0,0,0,,Não posso seguir em frente sem clamar\N vingança contra esses imbecis!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.68,0:15:25.88,Main,,0,0,0,,Luffy, desvie delas!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.88,0:15:26.66,Main,,0,0,0,,São balas explosivas!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.66,0:15:29.28,Main,,0,0,0,,Deixe comigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.67,0:15:33.34,Main,,0,0,0,,Por que você não usa as barreiras?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.37,0:15:40.49,Main,,0,0,0,,Ei, Bartolomeo!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.48,0:15:49.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Há um limite no tamanho da barreira que posso manter ao mesmo tempo...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.20,0:15:52.69,Main,,0,0,0,,E já usei tudo naquela escada!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.29,0:15:59.63,Main,,0,0,0,,Mas não tem problema!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.27,0:16:03.56,Main,,0,0,0,,Se isso ajudar o Luffy-senpai,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.94,0:16:07.19,Main,,0,0,0,,Não me importo de morrer!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.22,0:16:11.60,Main,,0,0,0,,Esse cara não tem jeito...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.60,0:16:15.59,Main,,0,0,0,,Vou lutar ao seu lado até que você possa usar as barreiras, então aguente firme!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.22,0:16:22.19,Main,,0,0,0,,Esses bonecos não têm delicadeza alguma!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.27,0:16:24.59,Main,,0,0,0,,Cinco Mano!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.59,0:16:25.23,Main,,0,0,0,,Spank!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.42,0:16:34.81,Main,,0,0,0,,Sei como você se sente,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.81,0:16:35.87,Main,,0,0,0,,Gallo-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.80,0:16:43.61,Main,,0,0,0,,Nosso capitão...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.25,0:16:47.73,Main,,0,0,0,,...merece que arrisquemos...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.60,0:16:49.84,Main,,0,0,0,,...nossas vidas!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.58,0:17:19.82,Main,,0,0,0,,Luffy sempre é a arma secreta \Nque nos leva à vitória!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.89,0:17:25.19,Main,,0,0,0,,Mil Fleur!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.84,0:17:27.36,Main,,0,0,0,,Mão Gigante!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.01,0:17:49.35,Main,,0,0,0,,Não vou deixar que coloquem\N as mãos em Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.35,0:17:50.84,Main,,0,0,0,,Isso mesmo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.84,0:17:55.85,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,300)}{\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170\fad(200,200)}CIDADE ACÁCIA\NSABO VS. ALMIRANTE FUJITORA
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.86,0:17:58.47,Main,,0,0,0,,Você é um cara muito estranho.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.47,0:18:03.04,Main,,0,0,0,,Eu achava que seu objetivo era\N nos manter à distância.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.04,0:18:06.07,Main,,0,0,0,,Quanto tempo mais você vai continuar fingindo?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.07,0:18:08.46,Main,,0,0,0,,Nossa...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.46,0:18:14.71,Main,,0,0,0,,Como você pode ver, preciso que\N não sejam muito duros comigo...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.71,0:18:17.15,Main,,0,0,0,,Eu não discrimino.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.15,0:18:19.45,Main,,0,0,0,,Você me assusta.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.45,0:18:23.68,Main,,0,0,0,,Acho que não é à toa que você é conhecido como o segundo em comando do Exército Revolucionário.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.68,0:18:28.05,Main,,0,0,0,,Mas minha posição me obriga a fazer isso.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.05,0:18:30.65,Main,,0,0,0,,Entenda, por favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.39,0:18:32.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Gravitou!{Espada da gravidade, Gravispada}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.13,0:18:40.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Mouko!{Tigre feroz}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.24,0:18:55.22,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,Gravidade horizontal?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.95,0:19:00.21,Main,,0,0,0,,Sim!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.21,0:19:02.21,Main,,0,0,0,,Isso é exatamente o que eu esperava dele!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.04,0:19:06.92,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,O que esse cara está planejando?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.43,0:19:25.88,Main,,0,0,0,,Isso é um jogo de tudo ou nada.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.88,0:19:30.51,Main,,0,0,0,,E estou decidido a arriscar minha vida nele.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.26,0:19:31.98,Main,,0,0,0,,Mas...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.88,0:19:38.66,Main,,0,0,0,,...se você perder os dados, o jogo terá\N acabado antes mesmo de começar.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.75,0:19:43.60,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,480)}{\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170\fad(100,0)}CAMPO DE FLORES\NMESETA DO PALÁCIO REAL\NQUARTO NIVEL
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.11,0:19:51.07,Main,,0,0,0,,Você é uma desgraça, Rebecca!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.60,0:19:52.71,Main,,0,0,0,,O que está acontecendo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.71,0:19:54.21,Main,,0,0,0,,Por que você está fugindo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.21,0:19:56.78,Main,,0,0,0,,Por que não está lutando?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.78,0:19:59.28,Main,,0,0,0,,Você é uma gladiadora!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.28,0:20:02.78,Main,,0,0,0,,Eu pensei que você tinha vindo para me matar!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.78,0:20:07.75,Main,,0,0,0,,No coliseu, eu poderia dar um bom \Nespetáculo às suas custas, mas...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.16,0:20:11.39,Main,,0,0,0,,...se você não pode lutar,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.10,0:20:14.50,Main,,0,0,0,,já deu tudo o que podia!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.70,0:20:41.36,Main,,0,0,0,,Vou acabar...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.36,0:20:43.13,Main,,0,0,0,,...com você.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.71,0:20:47.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Não, espere...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.72,0:20:51.84,Main,,0,0,0,,Você prefere uma pistola, não é?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.70,0:20:55.15,Main,,0,0,0,,Porque Scarlett...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.93,0:20:59.40,Main,,0,0,0,,...morreu diante de uma pistola!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.90,0:21:02.00,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,Socorro!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.48,0:21:06.74,Main,,0,0,0,,Soldado-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.75,0:21:10.15,Main,,0,0,0,,Rebecca!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.12,0:21:16.65,Main,,0,0,0,,Você é...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.82,0:21:19.82,Main,,0,0,0,,...Kyros!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.69,0:21:24.77,Main,,0,0,0,,Não vou deixar que você tire...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.77,0:21:27.37,Main,,0,0,0,,...outro membro da minha família!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.78,0:21:32.90,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Esta é a estátua de um homem lendário.{634}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.53,0:21:36.86,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Ele é o gladiador mais forte de\N toda a história do Coliseu Corrida.{634, modificado um pouco}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.12,0:21:59.63,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Não pude proteger sua mãe,\Nmas vou protegê-la com minha vida.{651}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.43,0:22:01.90,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Fique forte!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.57,0:22:04.18,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)}Rebecca!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.75,0:22:12.34,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,Pai...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.34,0:22:14.82,Main,,0,0,0,,Me perdoe, Rebecca.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.54,0:22:18.01,Main,,0,0,0,,Sendo um brinquedo sem futuro,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.61,0:22:21.59,Main,,0,0,0,,não pude fazer nada \Nalém de te ensinar a lutar!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.23,0:22:26.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Embora eu soubesse que você era alguém\N gentil, como sua mãe.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.11,0:22:30.96,Main,,0,0,0,,Mas isso acaba hoje!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.96,0:22:31.61,Main,,0,0,0,,O quê?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.93,0:22:34.42,Main,,0,0,0,,Já...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.03,0:22:37.41,Main,,0,0,0,,...não precisará mais lutar.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.51,0:22:49.65,Main,,0,0,0,,O que você quer dizer com isso, Kyros?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.65,0:22:52.45,Main,,0,0,0,,Quero dizer que hoje...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.45,0:22:54.89,Main,,0,0,0,,...acertarei as contas com todos vocês!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.04,0:23:07.54,Main,,0,0,0,,Maldito monstro!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.56,0:23:15.48,Main,,0,0,0,,Rebecca!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.15,0:23:20.82,Main,,0,0,0,,Será...?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.99,0:23:30.62,Main,,0,0,0,,Rebecca!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.63,0:23:33.96,Main,,0,0,0,,Lucy!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.93,0:23:41.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Rebecca!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.98,0:23:44.57,Main,,0,0,0,,A chave!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.08,0:23:46.07,Main,,0,0,0,,Lucy!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.85,0:23:49.39,Main,,0,0,0,,Ótimo, finalmente nos encontramos!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.54,0:24:01.70,Main,,0,0,0,,A chave!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.35,0:24:04.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Me dê, rápido!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.40,0:24:07.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Aqui está!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.80,0:24:12.53,Main,,0,0,0,,Rápido!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.09,0:24:14.77,Main,,0,0,0,,Rebecca!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.69,0:24:57.65,Main,,0,0,0,,Malditos!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.48,0:25:02.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Finalmente os alcançamos!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.38,0:25:04.84,Main,,0,0,0,,E finalmente estou livre!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.43,0:25:10.83,Main,,0,0,0,,Chegamos ao quarto nível, \Nonde está Mingo!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.83,0:25:13.17,Main,,0,0,0,,Ele está lá, né?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.17,0:25:14.39,Main,,0,0,0,,Sim.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.39,0:25:16.64,Main,,0,0,0,,Law! Chapéu de Palha!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.23,0:25:18.13,Main,,0,0,0,,Diamante...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.31,0:25:26.41,Main,,0,0,0,,Desculpe, pessoal...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.41,0:25:29.11,Main,,0,0,0,,Estou ocupado com esse cara.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.85,0:25:34.08,Main,,0,0,0,,Vocês poderiam cuidar do Doflamingo por mim?!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.94,0:25:36.69,Main,,0,0,0,,{\pos(320,700)}Claro!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.94,0:25:36.69,Secondary,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,700)}Claro!
